                        <p style="font-size:13px;">
                            <Span style="font-size:16px;">[Customer Service Center Description]</Span><br />
                            We provide "return service" and no replacement process is provided. Please correct orders for the correct products directly, save the time spent sending back and forth, and avoid waiting for out of stock. If you want to apply for a return, you can refer directly to "7-11 Return Application Process" and "Facilitate Dakang Return Application Process" . You do not need to wait for customer service reply and you can apply for a return online immediately. Other details, please refer to the return, refund Frequently Asked Questions<br />
