                            The question has been sent and the customer service reply. Please check the period under [Customer Service Record Inquiry] below. ( Customer service records provide information for the last six months only)
                        </p>
                        <div id="customer">
                            <form action="~/Customer/create" method="post" v-show="isLogin">
